      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Silkflex Polymers IPO<!-- --> is a <b>SME<!-- --> <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> of <!-- -->3482000<!-- --> equity shares</b> of the face value of ₹<!-- -->10<!-- --> aggregating up to ₹<!-- -->18.11<!-- --> Crores. The issue is priced at <span>₹52 per share</span>. The minimum order quantity is <!-- -->2000<!-- -->.</p><p>The <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> <b>opens on <!-- -->May 7, 2024</b>, and <b>closes on <!-- -->May 10, 2024</b>.</p><p>Bigshare Services Pvt Ltd<!-- --> is the registrar for the <!-- -->IPO<!-- -->. The shares are proposed to be listed on <!-- -->NSE SME<!-- -->.</p></div>"
